Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周終於到修學旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.54,0:01:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去京都 四日三夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必需品和注意事項大家自己看指南
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都的女生 應該很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}聽到了 別興奮過頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你無緣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計說了也沒用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被其他學校的人搭訕的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連自己學校的人都沒戲 還想外校的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的修學旅行 我還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好玩的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上還會輪流說自己心上人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心上人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心上人就是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可告人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可告人×N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田是不是第一次去京都啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古都啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒店肯定也充滿歷史情調
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去開房吧 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有詛咒說修學旅行好上的 很快就散的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我跟小須田只需要打一炮就行了 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把鉛筆跟吸管搞錯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動搖得很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H00E1B80F&}萬歲！修學旅行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻沒能單獨在一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 修學旅行是咋樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是集體活動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難跟小山田二人世界哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然能理解你想跟她再親一次的心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦 ~ 雖然想啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥知道我們親過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒提起過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親第二次之前 還有更重要的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認真向人家表白過沒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你這樣子 無論過多久 都只是曖昧關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人啊 個個都希望對方把心意說出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出來...對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都沒考慮過山田的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要接受了 親嘴什麼的想上就上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想上就上...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奸笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來 這話題是純還是不純啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛巾化妝水 刷牙套裝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 有好好在準備嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 京都的導遊手冊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}京都酒店導遊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ha ha ha這是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第14號線 7點40分發車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 好睏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田 你趁現在先好好謳歌一下純潔的青春吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為三天後 你的童子功就會被我廢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修學旅行晚上的鹹濕話題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從聽話人變成發言人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被人拿來當話題的 這都不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and Gentlemen we will soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 去京都吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是在路上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香蕉算點心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 還有醋拌海帶巧克力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 超難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要溫熱咖啡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服務員 我要啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來有人想馬上就退學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy過頭最後倒大霉的傢伙 還真有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:04:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小須田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田 我們也要拍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你郵箱地址 過後給我發哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 這不是數碼相機啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田 我們也要 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田那傢伙 別以為自己是負責拍照的就很受歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是全都是京都名產啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田 幫我把行李放上架子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田 幫我揉肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是沒誤會 不過...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為啥感覺也很不爽...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人心真複雜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是電影村的小冊子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 去年我媽去過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 好不好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說玩得相當happy來著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修學旅行真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對話自然而然就多起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的台詞也比平常多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過表白就難了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不能跟她單獨在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田也幫我們拍一拍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:05:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拍得好看點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還沒有表白的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田 來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別老拍別人 也留幾張自己的照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 我幫你跟山田拍一張
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰 誰要跟那種愛誤會的叛徒拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼所謂 大家都在拍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...想拍 想跟山田一起拍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 站起來排一塊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只此一張哦 我特別開恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是修學旅行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拍了哦 笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去旅館了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人都齊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一天是集體活動 沒辦法開溜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找了好久 機會都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清水寺也不是很高嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對古人來說可是劃時代的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到京都觀個毛光啊 都不想想我這邊這麼辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古都千年的歷史都比不上打炮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待去泡溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道京都料理是怎樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想 說到京都的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京懷石料理 家常菜 京都點心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都的食物太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田才不是那種被食物支配的人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得自己像個傻瓜一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他才一直沒察覺我的心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮野你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹下 你胸又大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 笨蛋 在摸哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生應該會幹這些吧 小須田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小 小須田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大...你這傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 來比鳥大賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生那邊 應該會這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妄想？ 剛才那些話全是你的妄想？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關燈啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好好睡覺 備戰明天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等好久了 修學旅行夜晚 當然就是鹹濕話題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 竹下 你的頭炮是啥感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎麼突然說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice 三鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:09:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實她都沒詳細告訴過我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹下 你跟現任男友很長久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被鎖定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算防守森嚴的女人也會被氣氛壓倒 赤裸裸地激烈告白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是修學旅行的妙趣所在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光說我一個 太狡猾了 三鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我還沒試過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃...那就換片瀨的來說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得你頭炮是在酒店打的來著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 你不是知道的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒店？ 該不會穿著校服就進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說就是啦 不能被人隨便捏造啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鄉 山田 你們過後給我記著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…最開始首先是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你們還不快點睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹下她啊 為了紀念初中畢業到男朋友的房聞...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來 片瀨又咋樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:09:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想多瞭解山田一點...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如她喜歡什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然表白也很重要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣跟她一起行動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起觀賞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起感受也是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊是本殿 那邊是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來她喜歡寺廟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人來的好後院
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶小須田來這裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎麼叫他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 用短信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦跟往常不一樣 能坦白傳達自己的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18}標題 建立肉體關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.97,0:10:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18}現在能不能單獨見面？\N一起打炮吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短信？ 誰發的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 短信求交配的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刪掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 趕緊回我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 估計一輩子都不會回你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家一起坐禪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅散煩惱 不被雜念困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心神渙散的人 就打一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打以後 要行禮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挨打了還要行禮？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不盡 女王大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩惱來得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒機會向山田表白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 只要能表白的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好開心 推倒我吧 小須田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有沒煩惱啊 這個猶豫不決的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念沒有一絲紊亂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位少女 已經領會禪之道了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:12:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 啊 ~ 哥哥 ~ 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓山田說不出話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 雖然內心的煩惱在渦旋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻毫不洩露出外頭 恐怖的精神力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.30,0:12:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗話說 人的煩惱有108種
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過拋除煩惱 就會看到自己真正追求的路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己真正追求的路...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 打炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 跟小須田 打炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害！沒有絲毫迷惘 這一位已經悟道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拜！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家左邊看到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼印觀光 京都支社大廈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.43,0:13:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們給我聽導遊小姐解說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒能跟他獨處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們走快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木筏觀光以後 就要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連有沒有表白機會都不知道...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來這三天 跟小須田一點進展都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 在船上誘惑他的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在回程電車上說不定...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 我已經把持不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 得快點上船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拋棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H00E1B80F&}山田、我喜……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:13:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路吵架的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 兩位客人把船包下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 就我們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誘惑小須田的絕好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我傻嘛我 區區小須田 牽個手就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算能跟她獨處了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚴格來說不算是二人世界啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種景色優美的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修學旅行這算是最後一站
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯過這個機會 大概到畢業都表白不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就擦肩而過 十年左右過後...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰 你認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:14:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 新來的 不准偷懶！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 我不要那種未來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 手 得牽手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄地...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就摸那裡？！不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有回去（青蛙）了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}蛙巖(笑)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不是冷笑話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣結束好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這麼遠的地方 兩人獨處卻什麼都沒發生就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田就沒所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中的修學旅行 一生只有一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 我喜...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前就對你...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.06,0:15:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田這種笨蛋就給我掉下河吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}電視機前的好孩子千萬不要模仿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修學旅行就結束了啊 太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想跟女生搞好一點關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒戲沒戲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來也沒能跟其他學校的女生搭訕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無斬獲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}喂 山田...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來 整個修學旅行跟小須田毫無進展
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 聽說你跟小須田兩個木筏觀光來著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 我跟那種挫男會發生什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對不起 太好了 什麼都沒發生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥要生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田 別這麼鬱悶啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是能跟山田一起 已經很榮幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這叫身份不相配
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這肉真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份不相配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以山田才會那麼生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這種人表白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定只會給她添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:17:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須由 沒事吧 沒食慾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉 我要了行麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在自己這邊 友情也不咋樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到東京 要不要到我家玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 可以啊 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵個毛 修學旅行的情侶馬上就散的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不想服輸也別那麼大聲啊 雖然是挺慘的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 看那樣子是沒發生好事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就很開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還認識了其他學校的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還買了禮物給哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 宮野 買了好多手信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 給家人的 香月姐的 給小須田的也買了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真的要給他的話 就是怪人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 三鄉有沒碰到什麼好事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問得好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他學校的男生跟我搭話了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就是問 金閣寺是那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:18:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}東京 ~ 東京 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.77,0:18:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解散 別到處亂跑直接回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 到家之前都還算修學旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹下 陪我去借可樂消愁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 過後我有約
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人嗎 是要會情郎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 我是松尾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後 什麼都沒發生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田不是喜歡我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得好愚蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是換個目標吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...小須田？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我一班電車麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來換乘前就在追你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要救差點被人潮擠倒的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被人誤會成癡漢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像小須田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田原來在追我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田原來在追我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼跟你說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管 對你又沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.27,0:19:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前就對你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 對你 對你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜！喜一一！喜一一！歡...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 我成功了 終於成功表白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然樣子很遜...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就清爽了 無論山田有什麼回覆 都能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點怕...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能聽清
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,su su
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.48,0:20:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透明內衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裸王？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 應該是「喜歡」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.57,0:20:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是特意追上我都要說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死小須田 不自量力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噁心死了 你這個攝影宅跑腿男
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要遮羞也不用這麼激動...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過嘛 這已經跟能打炮無疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.67,0:20:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是有那麼點開心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 等等 說不定其實完全不是那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別素顏朝天了 皮膚都開裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話 死小須田
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打完炮後給我記著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之還是很想幹一場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,su？ su呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是 「好色鬼」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又或者是「色狼」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有不喜歡上我的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你要怎麼回覆他？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？ 回覆？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家都表白了 你也得給個答覆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如「我也喜歡你」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 為啥我要說這話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這時候還嘴硬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.05,0:21:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又或者給他發張朋友卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮 炮友卡的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.80,0:21:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮友不是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 要說討厭他麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是逼太緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 說討厭他的話 不就打不成炮了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表白是表白了 不知道有沒把心意傳達給她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.32,0:21:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得認真問問
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 我怎麼逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川流不息 然其水非原水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（*出自《方丈記》）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮沫漂於積水 此消彼起未可久存…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.47,0:22:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小須田 有些話想跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.14,0:22:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果方便的話 午休在社團活動室等你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.15,0:22:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.33,0:22:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是回覆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.63,0:22:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才知道是喜歡還是討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想打炮罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.01,0:22:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田這笨蛋！
